text: Kuselyarovo () is a rural locality (a village) in Arkaulovsky Selsoviet, Salavatsky District, Bashkortostan, Russia. The population was 171 as of 2010. There are 4 streets. == Geography == It is located 37 km from Maloyaz, 9 km from Arkaulovo. == References == Category:Rural localities in Salavatsky District
title: Kuselyarovo
